    <title>Palette - proud of our new cafe/bar</title>
    <link rel="alternate" href="https://zurich4u.ch/2015/09/28/palette-proud-of-our-new-cafe-bar.html"/>
    <id>https://zurich4u.ch/2015/09/28/palette-proud-of-our-new-cafe-bar.html</id>
    <published>2015-09-28T09:15:39Z</published>
    <updated>2015-10-26T20:48:40+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Article Author</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="row"&gt;
  &lt;img class="pull-left img-responsive img-thumbnail article" src="/images/cb834474eb727b3941077df30daaf030.jpeg" /&gt;
  &lt;div class="article"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;div&gt;
        The Palette on Schützengasse 7, right on Bahnhofstrasse is offering healthy breakfast, homemade smoothies, Italian Espresso and Cappuccino. Mediterranean lunch and dinner snacks such as couscous with apricots, fennel feta and pomegranates, chicken pastis, meatballs with tomatoes and oriental spices, home made graved lox with soybeans, figs pecorino and basil. 
      &lt;/div&gt; 
      &lt;div&gt; 
       &lt;br&gt; 
      &lt;/div&gt; 
      &lt;div&gt;
        Andy&amp;rsquo;s special drink creations such as vodka with dark chocolate, just to mention one, are legendary. 
      &lt;/div&gt; 
      &lt;div&gt; 
       &lt;br&gt; 
      &lt;/div&gt; 
      &lt;div&gt;
        The atmosphere is very stylish and relaxed. 
      &lt;/div&gt; 
      &lt;div&gt; 
       &lt;br&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
    
  &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;div class="article"&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span/&gt; 
      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
  &lt;/div&gt;
