    &lt;p&gt;&lt;span/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bare foot bar is the place with the most magnificent setting for chilling on a summer evening. It is housed in the Frauenbadi, which as the name says, is a women only public bath during the day. Every Thursday, Friday and Saturday after 20.00 it is transformed into a bar for both sexes. The dress code is strict: barefoot. Wednesday (Fish dinner) , Thursday (Bar), Sunday (Dance) 20.00 until 24.00 &lt;a href="http://www.barfussbar.ch/"&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.barfussbar.ch/"&gt;http://www.barfussbar.ch/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; 
